  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Infection and inflammation is related to increased encephalopathy of prematurities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Animal studies have verified intravenous immunoglobin can reduce brain injury. However, no
      studies in preterm infants were reported.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
